Arguments.Name: in_Flow
Arguments.Tooltip: Overwrites the flow configuration by this one. Can be Producer, Consumer or Hybrid.

Arguments.Name: in_OrchestratorFolderName
Arguments.Tooltip: Overwrites the default Folder Name defined in the configuration files by this one.

Arguments.Name: in_QueueName
Arguments.Tooltip: Overwrites the default QueueName defined in the configuration files by this one.

Arguments.Name: in_ConfigPathToMerge
Arguments.Tooltip: Allows define an external configuration file to be merged during bot execution. If a Flow or a QueueName is defined in the file, it will be overwritten by the dedicated in_Flow and in_QueueName arguments if they are specified.
